one</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Skyreach\" title=\"Skyreach\">Skyreach</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Spottswood\" title=\"Spottswood\">Spottswood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Starfall\" title=\"Starfall\">Starfall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Stinkwater\" title=\"Stinkwater\">Stinkwater</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tor\" title=\"Tor\">Tor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vaith\" title=\"Vaith\">Vaith</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Water_Gardens\" title=\"Water Gardens\">Water Gardens</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wyl_(castle)\" title=\"Wyl (castle)\">Wyl</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Yronwood\" title=\"Yronwood\">Yronwood</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Ruins</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shandystone</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_joy\" title=\"Tower of joy\">Tower of joy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vulture%27s_Roost\" title=\"Vulture&#39;s Roost\">Vulture's Roost</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Locations</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Boneway\" title=\"Boneway\">Boneway</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brimstone\" title=\"Brimstone\">Brimstone</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Broken_Arm\" title=\"Broken Arm\">Broken Arm</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Greenblood\" title=\"Greenblood\">Greenblood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Prince%27s_Pass\" title=\"Prince&#39;s Pass\">Pri